<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.2">
<l>tiruvuṭampu vāṉcuṭarcen tāmaraikaṇ kaikamalan</l>
<l>tiruviṭamē mārva mayaṉiṭamē koppū</l>
<l>ḻoruviṭamu mentai perumāṟ karaṉēyō</l>
<l>voruviṭamoṉ ṟiṉṟiyeṉ ṉuḷkalan tāṉukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of him who mingled with my heart without any place that is renounced</l>
<l>the luminous body is of celestial lustre, red lotusses the eyes, the hand lotusses,</l>
<l>[his] chest is the place of Śrī, [his] navel the place of the unborn one</l>
<l>– is there also a place for Hara on the great lord, our father?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
